| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-1586 — Recovery Inhibition (IMNCrew)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: bb69610f-c4ed-5838-969b-2ec1c25e7e51"
